bring us as his personal guests.

04:29.930 --> 04:30.896
Will Chloe be there?

04:30.964 --> 04:32.731
Of course.

04:32.800 --> 04:35.467
Oh, I think I'm coming down
with something.

04:35.536 --> 04:36.668
- Katie.
- If you want,

04:36.737 --> 04:39.871
I will really commit
and eat a dirty tissue.

04:39.940 --> 04:41.273
