05:37.931 --> 05:40.999
Oh, sorry, hon, I'm already four deep.

05:42.736 --> 05:45.337
Let's see "Trois Souvenirs
De Ma Jeunesse."

05:45.405 --> 05:46.905
It's a French film
about an anthropologist

05:46.974 --> 05:49.407
