09:00.146 --> 09:01.345
So many.

09:01.414 --> 09:02.346
Oh.

09:05.084 --> 09:07.351
<i>I need to find a way
to get Chloe out of my life.</i>

09:07.420 --> 09:08.886
<i>Maybe I'll try the strategy</i>

09:08.955 --> 09:10.721
<i>they used to win
the Battle of Ridgefield,</i>

